Language: en

00:00:08.929 --> 00:00:16.930
Encompassing 300 acres of breath-taking beauty,
the Seascape Resort offers its guest easy

00:00:16.930 --> 00:00:25.590
access to pristine sugar white beaches, a
sprawling on-site golf course, fishable fresh

00:00:25.590 --> 00:00:34.600
water lakes, wandering bike and walking paths,
several delectable dining choices, and a variety

00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:37.160
of accommodation offerings.

00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:43.000
Soaring high into the sky is the largest of
the vacation rental buildings at Seacape,

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:47.400
the towers of Ariel Dunes I &amp; II.

00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:54.590
Featuring oversized lagoon style pools and
on-site dining at Cabana CafÃ©, you will be

00:00:54.590 --> 00:01:01.250
pleasantly surprised that condos offered at
Ariel Dunes are both well priced, and allow

00:01:01.250 --> 00:01:04.290
year round nightly rentals.

00:01:04.290 --> 00:01:11.000
Closer to the beach and staggered to the east
of Ariel Dunes is the neighboring complex,

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.610
Surfside Resort.

00:01:12.610 --> 00:01:19.830
This 16 story architecturally stunning building
is perched just across Scenic Gulf Drive from

00:01:19.830 --> 00:01:24.860
the sand, and offers a large selection of
amenities.

00:01:24.860 --> 00:01:33.369
Multiple pools, hot tubs, dining options,
a sports court, tennis, a fitness center,

00:01:33.369 --> 00:01:38.820
a private sky-bridge to the beach, and so
much more!

00:01:38.820 --> 00:01:43.860
Caressing the long Seascape beach and its
emerald green waters is an upscale complex,

00:01:43.860 --> 00:01:45.740
the Majestic Sun.

00:01:45.740 --> 00:01:51.850
Front and center with spectacular views, this
vacation destination offers in an indoor/outdoor

00:01:51.850 --> 00:01:59.510
pool, an additional outdoor pool, multiple
hot tubs, and a fitness center with a view.

00:01:59.510 --> 00:02:07.439
Accommodations offered include 1, 2, &amp; 3 bedroom
fully stocked condos as well as larger penthouse

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:08.509
units.

00:02:08.509 --> 00:02:16.489
Located discreetly next door to the Majestic
Sun is a private gated complex, The Empress.

00:02:16.489 --> 00:02:23.169
This low-occupancy condominium only offers
a handful of units per floor and features

00:02:23.169 --> 00:02:27.299
the largest standard floor plans on the resort.

00:02:27.299 --> 00:02:32.739
The Empress also hosts a lake-side pool &amp; hot
tub.

00:02:32.739 --> 00:02:38.700
Along the shores of the Seacape Resort guests
will enjoy the newly completed promenade with

00:02:38.700 --> 00:02:42.680
palm trees and multiple walkovers paralleling
the 2,000 linear feet of the powder white

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:44.030
sand.

00:02:44.030 --> 00:02:50.500
Access to so many water activities...soar
through the skies on a parasail, kayak or

00:02:50.500 --> 00:02:57.680
experience heart pounding wave runner action-
all without ever setting foot off the resort.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:03:04.010
At the western end of the Seascape beach is
The Whale's Tail restaurant and bar, which

00:03:04.010 --> 00:03:08.760
has a covered and open decks right on the
water, positioning you ideally to take in

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:09.760
all the action.

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:18.010
If golf is on the agenda, the par 71 eighteen
hole Seascape Golf Club is on the resort,

00:03:18.010 --> 00:03:24.510
featuring 6100 yards of play, and offering
players of all levels a chance to swing their

00:03:24.510 --> 00:03:26.110
clubs.

00:03:26.110 --> 00:03:33.199
Optimally located, the Seacape Resort offers
easy access to just about everything.

00:03:33.199 --> 00:03:40.290
Silver Sands, the nation's largest Designer
Outlet is literally just a few minutes away.

00:03:40.290 --> 00:03:46.999
The upscale restaurants and retail shops at
Grand Boulevard in Sandestin are nearby as

00:03:46.999 --> 00:03:50.949
is the magical Village of Baytowne Wharf.

